## Third-party components

This project orchestrates several third-party software components, each
distributed under its own license:

- Wine (stable) — LGPL-2.1-or-later. https://www.winehq.org/
- Winetricks — LGPL-2.1-or-later. https://github.com/Winetricks/winetricks
- DXMT — zlib. https://github.com/3Shain/dxmt
- GStreamer runtime — LGPL-2.1. https://gstreamer.freedesktop.org/
- Homebrew — BSD-2-Clause. https://brew.sh/
- Steam client (installed on demand by the user) — subject to the
  Steam Subscriber Agreement. https://store.steampowered.com/subscriber_agreement/
  This repository does not redistribute any Steam binaries; the
  installer is fetched from the official Valve CDN at runtime.

This repository neither redistributes nor wraps any of the above binaries.
Each is either installed via its upstream distribution channel (Homebrew
cask, GitHub Releases) or downloaded from the vendor at setup time.
